headline: 2 Dividend Stocks to Buy and Never Sell
summary: Johnson & Johnson has an impressive streak of payout increases, indicating a robust business.  Merck is facing challenges, but it can overcome them through innovation.  There are excellent reasons to invest in dividend stocks, including the fact that they typically outperform their non-dividend-paying peers in delivering strong market returns over long periods.
